"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-snoop-dogg-carries-olympic-torch-before-paris-2024-opening-ceremony\", \"text\": \"SAINT DENIS, SEINE-SAINT-DENIS, FRANCE - JULY 26: American rapper Snoop Dogg is seen carrying the Olympic flame during the torch relay ahead of the Summer Olympic Games Paris 2024 on July 26, 2024 in the Saint-Denis commune of Paris, France. (Photo by Remon Haazen/Getty Images)  Getty Images  Snoop Dogg has always known how to make his presence felt. He did just that as torchbearer, carrying the Olympic flame ahead of Friday's Opening Ceremony in Paris. The hip-hop legend brought the torch through Saint-Denis, a suburb north of Paris and home to the Stade de France Olympic Stadium. With the Paris Games primed to take off, Snoop Dogg is preparing for his role as a special correspondent for NBC and Peacock, where he will attend games, visit athletes, and report on air with Mike Tirico. Watch the historic Opening Ceremony live from the River Seine on Friday, July 26, onNBC and Peacock.  Take a look at some of the best moments from Snoop's torch relay trip.  Did somethin today. \\ud83d\\udcaf\\ud83d\\udc4a\\ud83c\\udfff\\ud83d\\udd25#FollowTheDoggpic.twitter.com/G4ugnUFssO  This is one time Snoop Dogg probably should not drop it like it's hot... \\ud83d\\ude05\\ud83d\\udd25\\ud83c\\udfa5@Paris2024|#ParisOlympicspic.twitter.com/NWdVUvf6QK  The stars are out for#Paris2024- Snoop Dogg and the Olympic torch! \\ud83e\\udd29#BBCOlympicspic.twitter.com/ItETe6SJfB  The#ParisOlympicsare cool, fool. \\ud83d\\udd25pic.twitter.com/VXEYGcutN1  The crossover we did not know we needed \\ud83e\\udd29-C'est donc \\u00e7a le multiverse \\ud83e\\udd29Suivez l'\\u00e9tape du jour en direct sur@FranceTV:https://t.co/TWcSUAw0vu#Paris2024@Olympics@SnoopDogg@NBCOlympics@TeamUSA\\ud83d\\udcf8 Paris 2024pic.twitter.com/E3Bf5pIuCi  Snoop Dogg is ready to VIBE at the#ParisOlympics! \\ud83d\\ude0e(\\ud83c\\udfa5:@SnoopDogg)pic.twitter.com/hnYlQhRF3W  U gots to do it!! \\ud83d\